      BUSINESS PROBLEM STATEMENT:

      BUSINESS PROBLEM STATEMENT:

      In [ ]:
      xxxxxxxxxx
       
      Walmart is a retail corporation which has more than 100 million customers worldwide.It operates grocery stores,departmental stores and a chain of supercenters.Now the company wants to know the customer behaviour with the help of the given data to increase the sales in the future.Data analysis with data visualisation can help them to identify in which category of cutomers they should focus and which category of cutomers purchasing more.
      First we should do some basic analysis to know the structure and characteristics of the each column.This can be done with help of the numpy and pandas functions.Mainly we should focus on  what type of variables of data we are working on,whether it is categorical or continuous variables.Treatment of each variable is diffrent.Categorical variables are those are in particular range i.e.  Gender and Marital_Status columns.Continuous variables are those which does not have any range and numerical i.e.Purchase.Other Variables apart from those like occupation and Product_Category can be both because they are numerical in range but the numbers are in particular range.We can convert those into categorical and can done basic analysis.
      Univariate and byvariate analysis helps to identify the relation between two variables.Data visualization adds a benefit to describe the analysis in a simple plot.We can start the analysis by answering a set of questions.For example:

      xxxxxxxxxx
       
      Confidence interval helps to find the population mean.It does not exactly give the value but it gives a range (start,end).
      Population mean lies in that specific range.It is calculated with the given sample.If the number of samples are more,confidence 
      interval gives most accurate range.If the samples are less,confidence interval may not be accurate.The width of the interval is 
      mostly decided by the business.Typically 90%, 95%, or 99%.99% confidence interval gives the most accurate range.

      Confidence interval helps to find the population mean.It does not exactly give the value but it gives a range (start,end). Population mean lies in that specific range.It is calculated with the given sample.If the number of samples are more,confidence interval gives most accurate range.If the samples are less,confidence interval may not be accurate.The width of the interval is mostly decided by the business.Typically 90%, 95%, or 99%.99% confidence interval gives the most accurate range.
